comments: Harris (BKN) sets the pick in Rozier's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Allen (BKN) makes marginal contact with Rozier (CHA) as he releases from the contact after setting the pick.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes marginal contact with Zeller's (CHA) body during the driving shot attempt.
Temple (BKN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Graham (CHA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Graham (CHA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Bridges (CHA) makes contact with Dinwiddie's (BKN) body during his shooting motion and affects his jump shot attempt.
Nwaba (BKN) briefly grasps Zeller (CHA) before sliding his hand off.
Pinson (BKN) briefly engages and disengages with Graham (CHA) off ball during the inbound.
Temple (BKN) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) and Temple (BKN) make marginal contact before Temple goes over the screen.
Graham (CHA) and Nwaba (BKN) make incidental contact with one another during the loose ball situation.
Dinwiddie (BKN) and Bridges (CHA) make incidental foot contact during the loose ball situation.
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
